4562:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
4563:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
