6073:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         TR2      HT2            LL_ADC_GetAnalogWDThresholds\n
6074:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         TR3      HT3            LL_ADC_GetAnalogWDThresholds\n
